roup is terminating its"],[8621,8842,"partnership with the Clement family."],[8879,9004,"The Maple Hotel project"],[9004,9129,"is back on the market."],[9250,9367,"You can't do that."]],"29":[[29,116,"You can't do that."],[116,241,"That's enough for tonight."],[287,408,"I'll excuse myself."],[688,746,"Oops."],[963,1013,"Wait, just-"],[1530,1722,"Bennett, that's my wife."],[1768,1893,"Think I got this."],[1918,2027,"Why don't you stay in your lane?"],[2027,2223,"No, you stay in your lane."],[2223,2314,"Don't forget,"],[2314,2510,"we're in the middle of a divorce."],[2556,2669,"Come home with me."],[2698,2765,"We need to talk."],[2765,2911,"There's nothing left to talk about."],[2911,3119,"And that's your home, not mine."],[3294,3520,"Your mother treated me like a servant"],[3532,3674,"for three years."],[3757,3895,"I was never welcome."],[3987,4091,"I don't want a home"],[4091,4225,"where I'm not wanted."],[4537,4633,"Are you really going to make"],[4633,4783,"this harder on the both of us?"],[4854,4925,"Me?"],[5000,5130,"Why don't you check in with your"],[5130,5271,"girlfriend over there?"]],"30":[[20,137,"I can't believe she has the"],[137,233,"power of veto"],[233,354,"of the Maple Project."],[354,529,"And nobody stood up to her!"],[567,800,"If Cornell loses this, what happens to us?"],[800,863,"No,"],[917,1034,"that's not possible."],[1034,1105,"The Maple Group"],[1105,1376,"CEO personally approved this."],[1384,1555,"Bennett can't override that."],[1589,1714,"Audrey's just bluffing."],[1722,1843,"She doesn't have the power to make"],[1843,1931,"that call."],[1947,2102,"You're so sharp, Cecilia."],[2164,2423,"You truly are perfect for Cornell."],[2527,2656,"You should be thanking her."],[2669,2857,"If it weren't for her, you wouldn't be here."],[3128,3199,"I'm gonna,"],[3199,3294,"I'm gonna get some air."],[5492,5680,"Still thinking about Audrey?"]],"31":[[250,408,"She is all over Bennett now,"],[408,592,"there's no way that's just business."],[613,717,"Bennett..."],[800,884,"is he the guy she was"],[884,1013,"talking about in her sleep?"],[1680,1835,"She looks kind of cute."],[2139,2248,"Babe."],[2293,2448,"She never called me bae!"],[2715,2902,"She acted like she loved me."],[2936,3053,"Was it all fake?"],[3432,3549,"Let's go, Cecilia."],[3586,3724,"There's something I have to do."],[3749,3787,"Wait."],[3803,3887,"Where are you going?"],[3887,4004,"Are you mad at me?"],[4149,4358,"I didn't want to leave you."],[4416,4617,"My parents forced me to."],[4617,4783,"Audrey took advantage of that."],[4783,4871,"You know that!"],[4871,4959,"Enough."],[5092,5205,"Just stop."],[5326,5543,"She betrayed you, Cornell."],[5638,5860,"Why can't you just let her go?"],[5947,6122,"You're not..."],[6122,6343,"really in love with her, are you?"]],"32":[[37,95,"No."],[162,412,"Cornell, I gave up everything for you."],[446,692,"I sacrificed my future, my leg."],[721,809,"You promised you would"],[809,934,"take care of me."],[1126,1222,"I haven't forgotten what you've"],[1222,1347,"done for me,"],[1388,1514,"and I'm going to keep my promise"],[1514,1589,"to you."],[1630,1835,"As soon as I secure my position"],[1851,1947,"as the Maple Hotel"],[1947,2047,"CEO,"],[2131,2327,"I will find a place for you in the company."],[2339,2560,"But Audrey will always be my wife."],[2644,2798,"That's not going to change."],[3236,3349,"Find Audrey."],[3407,3520,"I have to talk to her."],[3549,3737,"Audrey, I won't let you have him."],[3737,4041,"Cornell's wife will be me, and only me."],[5651,5743,"Hey, boss."],[5801,5972,"Still hung up on"],[5972,6064,"Cornell?"],[6081,6160,"No."],[6322,6460,"Well,"],[6460,6648,"you've drunk enough for three people."],[6648,6785,"When you're drowning,"],[6785,6902,"you don't forget"],[6902,7132,"the people that threw you a lifeline."],[7169,7336,"Hey, hey, hey, hey."],[7349,7482,"I think you've had enough, all right?"],[7899,8008,"I'm fine."],[8028,8170,"You know, I've decided,"],[8220,8416,"no more wasting time on him."],[8445,8575,"I'm moving on."],[8616,8746,"All right, well, that's good."],[8775,8896,"And the best way to"],[8896,9075,"forget about someone is to"],[9075,9221,"have a little fun."],[9234,9346,"And I've arranged something that"],[9346,9471,"I hope you like."],[9868,9955,"Wait..."],[10068,10268,"you got me two guys?"]],"33":[[16,196,"Only the two handsomest"],[196,375,"models in town."],[425,663,"Only the best for you, my dear Audrey."],[688,817,"Thanks, but, you know,"],[817,955,"I'm not interested."],[1038,1142,"Audrey,"],[1180,1372,"Cornell betrayed you with another woman"],[1372,1530,"while you were still married."],[1551,1672,"This is just"],[1672,1818,"drinks with a couple of"],[1818,1935,"good-looking guys."],[1947,2077,"Where's the harm in that?"],[2260,2435,"Somebody wants to dance."],[4020,4187,"I wonder how Cornell's gonna react"],[4187,4316,"when he sees his precious wife"],[4316,4521,"cheating in public."],[6519,6744,"Yeah, I never said you could touch me."],[6744,6915,"Audrey, what the hell are you doing?"]],"34":[[37,183,"I'm drunk,"],[183,279,"okay?"],[296,371,"What's next?"],[383,504,"Mr. Perfect,"],[504,621,"Cornell Clement,"],[621,746,"gracing a nightclub?"],[763,934,"I didn't think that was your scene."],[934,1038,"No, no, no, no."],[1038,1201,"Don't change the subject."],[1201,1288,"Do I have to remind you?"],[1288,1409,"We're still married."],[1430,1697,"How many times do I have to say this?"],[1705,1868,"We're getting a divorce,"],[1868,2014,"so stay out of my life!"],[2085,2268,"If Cecelia hadn't sent me this video,"],[2673,2794,"I would've never known you've been"],[2794,2957,"out with a bunch of random guys."],[2994,3169,"Since you trust Cecilia so much,"],[3169,3324,"why are you even here?"],[3361,3532,"I don't owe you an explanation."],[3570,3595,"Just-"],[3657,3716,"Bennett,"],[3737,3803,"I'm tired."],[3803,3887,"Let's go."],[4300,4458,"You're still mine, Audrey."],[4587,4650,"You think you can just"],[4650,4725,"go out with Bennett,"],[4725,4804,"a guy that"],[4804,4954,"will just sit there and watch you flirt"],[4954,5088,"with random guys right in front of him?"],[5088,5155,"Are you crazy?"],[5155,5334,"What the hell are you even saying?"],[5401,5467,"You"],[5467,5613,"decided not to be Mrs. Clement"],[5613,5701,"anymore."],[5776,5914,"Now you're out with Bennett,"],[5955,6106,"a guy who treats you like this?"],[6106,6268,"Are you really okay with that?"],[6356,6464,"Shut up!"]],"35":[[25,150,"I said stay out of my life!"],[187,266,"Come on,"],[266,346,"let's go."],[346,487,"Let go, we're done."],[508,588,"Back off, Cornell!"],[588,667,"Stop interfering-"],[813,938,"Why would I let her waste her time with"],[938,1030,"someone like you?"],[1180,1322,"Why the hell would she have ever loved"],[1322,1409,"someone like you?"],[2006,2039,"Stop!"],[2039,2135,"Both of you!"],[2498,2627,"I said stop!"]],"36":[[112,241,"I said stop!"],[850,971,"Are you okay?"],[971,1042,"Don't worry about me."],[1042,1117,"I'm fine."],[1176,1355,"Cornell, if you mess with Bennett again,"],[1355,1426,"I will expose"],[1426,1522,"everything you've done."],[1568,1680,"You think you have a future with"],[1680,1730,"this guy?"],[1776,1922,"He's the VP of the Maple Group!"],[1922,2052,"What's he gonna do with a divorcée"],[2052,2156,"who offers nothing?"],[2168,2394,"Can you just stop this nonsense?"],[2610,2719,"Nonsense?"],[2811,2894,"You are the one who's been"],[2894,3069,"running around here telling everybody"],[3069,3278,"that you're the CEO of the Maple Group!"],[3303,3440,"Do you even hear yourself?"],[3453,3570,"Even after everything,"],[3570,3716,"you still don't believe me,"],[3716,3787,"do you?"],[3820,3987,"Listen, cut ties with this guy,"],[3987,4091,"and come back to me."],[4099,4175,"I will forgive you,"],[4175,4300,"and smooth everything over."],[4300,4466,"Even if the CEO jumps in,"],[4466,4612,"I will protect you!"]],"37":[[12,83,"You?"],[112,229,"Forgive me?"],[287,383,"How generous."],[396,521,"Did you forget that you're the one"],[521,696,"cozying up to Cecilia?"],[734,855,"Let me make this clear."],[855,975,"There's no way in hell"],[975,1134,"I'm ever coming back to you!"],[1134,1259,"This isn't the place to talk about it."],[1259,1322,"Let's go home,"],[1322,1359,"all right?"],[1376,1484,"Go home?"],[1518,1618,"To what?"],[1647,1764,"Your mother's insults,"],[1764,1939,"your girlfriend's humiliation,"],[1939,2077,"and keep playing housekeeper"],[2077,2164,"for you?"],[2206,2402,"And maybe you can just cheat on me"],[2402,2556,"right in front of my face!"],[2556,2656,"There's nothing"],[2656,2865,"going on between Cecilia and I!"],[2873,3040,"I don't care!"],[3136,3282,"Let's get you to a hospital."],[3507,3591,"A hospital?"],[3661,3712,"No,"],[3712,3778,"great."],[3803,3928,"Audrey, I don't know if you've noticed,"],[3928,4112,"I'm just as hurt as he is!"]],"38":[[75,225,"We're done, Cornell."],[246,379,"Stop bothering me!"],[408,487,"You hurt her first,"],[487,617,"and the pain you put her through"],[629,717,"is a hundred times"],[717,834,"what you're experiencing."],[1134,1234,"Audrey!"],[1935,2077,"So this is your revenge, huh?"],[2093,2256,"You live with me in luxury,"],[2256,2381,"now you leave me here alone."],[2394,2598,"We are not getting a divorce,"],[2598,2706,"ever!"],[3478,3607,"Audrey?"],[3728,3841,"Audrey,"],[3841,3941,"you home?"],[5080,5176,"God."],[5313,5405,"Audrey!"],[6018,6177,"You keep saying your leg's fine,"],[6177,6277,"but I can tell you're in"],[6277,6448,"pain every time you stand up."],[6815,6998,"All right, I put the rest in your pocket."],[6998,7132,"Take one if it gets bad."]],"39":[[729,825,"Audrey,"],[967,1113,"you walk into my life,"],[1113,1305,"and now you leave me here,"],[1343,1426,"all alone."],[1743,1885,"Where have you been?"],[2010,2131,"Why are you so drunk?"],[2168,2306,"Cecilia's been worried sick"],[2306,2369,"about you. -Mom, how"],[2369,2581,"many more times do I have to tell you?"],[2656,2756,"I'm married."],[2781,2911,"I already have a wife!"],[2927,3157,"You are out of Audrey's league."],[3157,3286,"The only reason I went along"],[3286,3395,"with that marriage was because you"],[3395,3490,"hurt your leg and needed"],[3490,3653,"somebody to take care of you!"],[3666,3791,"I didn't know this is how you always"],[3791,3870,"thought of her."]],"40":[[141,279,"All she does is cook and clean."],[279,454,"She's basically a maid!"],[454,621,"Whatever you thought,"],[650,888,"I have never thought of that woman as"],[888,992,"my daughter-in-law."],[1080,1209,"Here the whole time I thought you"],[1209,1376,"treated her as family."],[1376,1468,"And maybe, I..."],[1559,1705,"Maybe I spoiled her because of it."],[1714,1785,"But..."],[2031,2127,"maybe I've"],[2143,2289,"been wrong this whole time, huh?"],[3432,3611,"You've reached the voicemail of-"],[4129,4200,"Cornell."],[4258,4329,"Cornell!"],[4362,4429,"Cornell!"],[4533,4750,"Is he actually in love with her?"]],"41":[[62,129,"No!"],[154,362,"No, I, I can't let that happen."],[433,583,"Maple Group's CEO will be at"],[583,696,"this auction."],[717,859,"If they find out Audrey canceled"],[859,1076,"the Maple Hotel deal without approval,"],[1105,1251,"she'll be ruined."],[1901,2002,"Audrey,"],[2102,2210,"everything is set up for your"],[2210,2306,"collaboration meeting with"],[2306,2385,"Mr. Adam."],[2448,2573,"Oh, and he invited"],[2573,2706,"you to join him on the hike."],[2706,2865,"He invited all the key players."],[2948,3115,"My injury, remember?"],[3115,3278,"I won't be able to hike anymore."],[3294,3361,"I'm so sorry."],[3361,3486,"I shouldn't have mentioned it."],[3561,3632,"Do you have the time?"],[3649,3737,"Yeah, of course."],[3887,3933,"Oh."],[4262,4408,"It's all in the past."],[4517,4696,"How could a woman so kind,"],[4696,4754,"capable,"],[4754,4842,"and beautiful"],[4842,5013,"end up with a jerk like Cornell?"]],"42":[[1447,1589,"My medication,"],[1589,1697,"it's in the bag."],[2761,2898,"Thank you, Audrey."],[3023,3140,"You've had this heart condition"],[3140,3265,"for a while now."],[3303,3470,"Why haven't you been to a hospital?"],[3582,3728,"I can't afford it."],[3762,3958,"My son has a heart condition."],[4008,4258,"I have to prioritize his treatment."],[4842,4967,"Here,"],[4967,5071,"take this."],[5105,5355,"Get the care you need for both of you."],[5355,5463,"I can't."],[5534,5588,"I can't."],[5588,5726,"You have your own struggles."],[5726,5826,"I can't take your money."],[5826,5968,"Please just take it."],[6122,6231,"There she is!"],[6423,6510,"Search her."]],"43":[[29,196,"What do you think you're doing here?"],[458,554,"Back up."],[617,838,"Cornell gave me a custom bracelet,"],[871,959,"and it's missing."],[1042,1180,"Someone saw you lurking around"],[1180,1263,"my office,"],[1263,1430,"and I think you took it."],[1438,1605,"Why would I even steal from you?"],[1626,1755,"I'm not interested."],[1797,1906,"If you think I took it,"],[1922,2006,"then prove it."],[2035,2185,"Stop throwing around baseless"],[2185,2298,"accusations."],[2331,2423,"Proof?"],[2515,2556,"Oh,"],[2569,2669,"I have proof."],[2669,2727,"Search her,"],[2727,2790,"now!"],[2907,3036,"Don't you dare touch me."],[3724,3937,"Here it is."]],"44":[[45,162,"This is my bracelet."],[208,358,"What do you have to say for yourself?"],[358,454,"I didn't take it."],[471,592,"Stop lying."],[704,880,"This is a custom bracelet,"],[880,1042,"something you could never afford."],[1071,1251,"Cornell had it made for me."],[1251,1393,"Is this your little"],[1409,1668,"revenge for losing him to me?"],[1951,2198,"He's not the only guy in the world, Cecilia."],[2248,2402,"You're the only one desperate enough"],[2402,2494,"to cling to Cornell"],[2494,2648,"like your life depends on it."],[2648,2844,"I wouldn't waste my time on revenge."],[2890,3082,"Then why was it in your pocket?"],[3378,3461,"I've heard enough."],[3461,3532,"Security,"],[3532,3607,"take her away."],[3624,3720,"I didn't steal anything,"],[3720,3841,"and I said don't touch me."],[3962,4029,"Really?"],[4170,4270,"You were with her the whole day."],[4270,4350,"Did she take it?"],[4504,4629,"Think very carefully"],[4650,4775,"before you answer."],[4875,4988,"I heard that you and your child"],[4988,5113,"have a heart condition."],[5192,5417,"If you testify for me and say that she"],[5417,5626,"stole my bracelet,"],[5643,5880,"I'll cover all of your medical expenses,"],[5880,6056,"you and your kid."],[6089,6164,"But..."],[6185,6318,"that's a lot of money."],[6431,6473,"Oh,"],[6493,6569,"don't worry."],[6598,6831,"I'm about to be the CEO's wife."],[6869,6961,"I can afford it."],[7344,7424,"Now,"],[7624,7912,"did she or didn't she steal my bracelet?"]],"45":[[454,608,"She, she stole it."],[767,925,"I said I would help you if you needed"],[925,1042,"money, Ashley."],[1071,1217,"Why are you lying for her?"],[1217,1363,"So sorry..."],[1426,1568,"But my child..."],[1593,1668,"Audrey,"],[1705,2014,"his medical bills are so much."],[2064,2185,"What you have,"],[2227,2356,"it won't cover it."],[2356,2464,"Just, just take it back."],[2464,2669,"No, this card has a million dollars on it."],[2669,2765,"That's more than enough for"],[2765,2882,"his treatments."],[2923,3069,"I know you mean well,"],[3069,3353,"but you work here every day."],[3465,3628,"Where would you get that kind of money?"],[3657,3728,"See?"],[3741,3903,"Even your co-workers know you're broke."],[3949,4074,"You can't even support yourself,"],[4074,4216,"and you try to play savior?"],[4241,4350,"Pathetic."],[4379,4667,"I'm so sorry, Audrey."],[4796,4904,"Stop whining."],[4971,5192,"I have all the evidence I need now,"],[5192,5401,"video and testimony."],[5451,5672,"Before I came here, I called Jonas Boyd,"],[5701,5905,"the deputy head of the charity auction."],[5947,6093,"He'll be here any minute."],[6168,6297,"Looking forward to see how you"],[6297,6431,"talk your way out of this one when he"],[6431,6514,"gets here."],[6539,6706,"The department charity head?"],[6706,6844,"Enjoy your 